- `evaluateCondition` in `dialogueBranch.ts` parses `has_relationship` values as `"npcId:minValue"` (e.g. `"elder-rowan:25"`) — splitting on `:` to extract both parts. This string-encoding pattern avoids needing a richer condition schema.
- The dialogue gating chain: `filterAvailableBranches` → `evaluateCondition` → `checkRelationshipCondition` → raw relationship map. Tests at each layer verify the full pipeline without needing integration mocks.
